IMPLEMENTATION OF THE CODE


1. Open the the tools for development of AVR microcontrollers and read carefully by clicking: "https://github.com/wykys/AVR-tools"

2. Type git clone https://github.com/wykys/AVR-tools" to make a local copy of the repository. 
3. Replace the main file found on this page.
4. Make the physical connection of the components
5. Open Terminal
6. Type "cd" and then the location of the repository.
7. Type "make build_and_flash"
8. VOILA


